Name: Fairytale Figurine: Pop-Up Paper Frog
Desc: A lively, leaf-green paper frog model that may be placed on a "Good Shelf" for display.\nThis model is reportedly based on Xudi himself, symbolizing the starting point of his modeling journey and representing his adventurous spirit. In spite of the challenges ahead, Xudi shall boldly "leap" around the world, creating more outstanding models wherever he goes!
